{"type": "article", "id": 11843, "title": "迷你可折叠键盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-09T11:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135748jE8HB0JvqbGU921X.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tWaytools 推出了一款简易的键盘，名为 “TextBlade”，它的折叠面积仅仅是一部 iPhone 6 的三分之一，而当拆开后可以满足基本的打字需求。键盘通过蓝牙和其他设备如手机，平板电脑等连接，内部有多点触控键盘技术。键盘通过 USB 充电，充一次可以满足一个月的使用时间。<a href=\"https://waytools.com/store\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135838Oyzol0CV3L2neI9k.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135838hqGJaPIKYECjLw1T.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"452\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135838qbAt8ZkJLsR7deCh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"456\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135839aAmfNHiZ3Vt15do7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"568\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}